com.commercetools.importapi.models.common

Interface ImportResource

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CategoryImport, CustomerImport, InventoryImport, OrderImport, PriceImport, ProductDraftImport, ProductImport, ProductTypeImport, ProductVariantImport
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CategoryImportImpl, CustomerImportImpl, ImportResourceImpl, InventoryImportImpl, OrderImportImpl, PriceImportImpl, ProductDraftImportImpl, ProductImportImpl, ProductTypeImportImpl, ProductVariantImportImpl

    public interface ImportResource

    A representation of the resource to import. Import resources are similar to commercetools draft types, but they only support key references. In general, import resources are more granular then the normal commercetools resource. They are optimized for incremental updates and therefore have a slightly different structure.
